{"title":"弹性布局和网格布局","date":"2019-05-17T16:00:00.000Z","slug":"layout-flex&grid","comments":true,"tags":["css"],"categories":["学习"],"updated":"2019-05-18T09:31:05.423Z","content":"<p>&emsp;&emsp;ie仅支持grid旧规范 == 许多新规范的属性无法使用(但是一家的edge是支持的)<br><a id=\"more\"></a></p>\n<h1 id=\"概述\">概述<a href=\"post/layout-flex&grid#概述\"></a></h1><blockquote>\n<p>flex：老子管儿子为主</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">display: flex;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>&emsp;&emsp;父元素定义<code>flex</code>之后，可继续加规定来告诉儿子们应该怎么摆好自己的位置</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>grid：儿子自由发挥为主</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">display: grid;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>&emsp;&emsp;父元素定义<code>grid</code>之后，儿子们自己来划分自己的地盘</p>\n<div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"/article-material/Layout-flex&amp;grid/1.png\" alt data-zoomable></p></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>两者都可以让我们抛开各个元素的细节定位，这也是我们为什么要用他们的原因</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"flex\">flex<a href=\"post/layout-flex&grid#flex\"></a></h1><p>在线调试：<a href=\"http://the-echoplex.net/flexyboxes\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://the-echoplex.net/flexyboxes</a></p>\n<p>语法介绍：<a href=\"http://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2015/07/flex-grammar.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2015/07/flex-grammar.html</a></p>\n<p>用途实例：<a href=\"http://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2015/07/flex-examples.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2015/07/flex-examples.html</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"grid\">grid<a href=\"post/layout-flex&grid#grid\"></a></h1><p>语法介绍：<a href=\"http://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2019/03/grid-layout-tutorial.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2019/03/grid-layout-tutorial.html</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"检验练习\">检验练习<a href=\"post/layout-flex&grid#检验练习\"></a></h1><p>如何知道自己是不是掌握了呢？试试这个小游戏吧（grid那个也可以算是在线调试）：</p>\n<p>flex：<a href=\"http://flexboxfroggy.com/#zh-cn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://flexboxfroggy.com/#zh-cn</a></p>\n<p>grid：<a href=\"http://www.css88.com/tool/gridgarden/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://www.css88.com/tool/gridgarden/</a></p>\n","next":{"title":"浏览器兼容（js）","slug":"browserCompatibility-js"},"link":"http://github.com/post/layout-flex&grid/","toc":[{"title":"概述","id":"概述","index":"1"},{"title":"flex","id":"flex","index":"2"},{"title":"grid","id":"grid","index":"3"},{"title":"检验练习","id":"检验练习","index":"4"}]}